Implementation task for Epic $epic_num - Quality assurance and production readiness.

## Technical Requirements
Detailed specifications in epic5-analysis.md and parent user story #$issue_num.

## Dependencies
- Epic 1-4 completed
- Quality assurance understanding

## References
- Parent User Story: #$issue_num
- Epic 5 Analysis: [epic5-analysis.md](https://github.com/o2alexanderfedin/telethon-architecture-docs/blob/main/features/voice-transcription/epic5-analysis.md)")

    gh project item-add 6 --owner o2alexanderfedin --url "$issue_url"
  done
done

echo "Created Epic 5.1-5.6 tasks")
